Text: It did work. But now, when the connection is set up with the client, there is a message that the client have an old version and needs to be updated. (connection still can be made) When you update instead, then Team Viewer won't start. (failed to load resource DLL, teamviewer_resource.dll). Even after disable the update, this message pops up
It worked for me with no issues, no errors as of yet.  I did a full uninstall (including settings) before I installed this version.
